Package com.composum.sling.clientlibs.handle

Class ClientlibResourceFolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.composum.sling.clientlibs.handle.ClientlibResourceFolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ClientlibElement
    public class ClientlibResourceFolder
extends Object
implements ClientlibElement
    Models a resource folder for a Clientlib - this can be the folder js/css directly below it, or a lower level folder.
